      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm 6 months pregnant and my sinus infection is getting really bad... like i can barely breathe through my nose and my head hurts so much. i have some Sudafed (pseudoephedrine) in the cabinet from before, is it okay if i take some to help clear things up? i really need to sleep.",
