      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know it's not ideal but i'm already in my second trimester (6 months), not the first. the bottle says it's fine for adults and i've heard some people say it's okay after the first trimester is over. if i just take one dose to get through the night so i can actually sleep, is it really that big of a deal? i'm just so miserable right now.",
